                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7435" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1164</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3094 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">未来已来：虚拟数字代言人能否为花西子带来新突破？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Future is Coming: Could Virtual Digital Endorsement Bring New Breakthroughs for Florasis?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">袁海霞，白琳，杜晶晶，叶江峰，徐海琴，陈俊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江宜格企业管理集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">花西子；虚拟数字代言人；明星代言人；虚拟主播；2023百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Florasis; Virtual digital endorsement; Celebrity endorsement; Virtual live-streamer</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智能时代的到来和元宇宙概念的爆发，使虚拟数字人成为未来传播的重要带动点和关键引爆点。本案例以虚拟数字代言人“花西子”的发展历程为主线，描述了企业基于创建百年文化品牌战略的愿景，借助技术发展的机会，创设虚拟数字代言人“花西子”的过程，进一步地通过描述花西子明星代言人和虚拟数字代言人的联合运营，来呈现其虚实结合的智能营销策略；最后，随着技术的发展，虚拟主播出现并被认为是打开元宇宙大门的最佳方式，对于已拥有虚拟数字代言人的花西子来说，是让“花西子”进入直播领域“一人分饰不同角色”，还是重新配置不同的虚拟数字人，成为困扰企业智能营销的一大难题。本案例旨在通过一个真实的案例引导学生思考：元宇宙时代企业如何合理布局虚拟数字代言人、有效处理其与明星代言人、虚拟主播的关系。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The emergence of the intelligent era and the explosion of the metaverse concept have made virtual digital humans an important driving force and key ignition point for future communication. This case study focuses on the development of virtual digital spokesperson &quot;Florasis&quot; and describes the process by which companies create the virtual digital spokesperson &quot;Florasis&quot; based on their vision of creating a hundred-year cultural brand strategy and leveraging opportunities for technological development. Furthermore, the case study presents the intelligent marketing strategy of combining Florasis&#39;s real celebrity spokesperson and virtual digital spokesperson through joint operations. Finally, with the development of technology, virtual anchors have emerged as the best way to open the door to the metaverse. For Florasis, who already has a virtual digital spokesperson, whether to let &quot;Florasis&quot; play different roles in the live broadcast field alone or to reconfigure different virtual digital humans has become a major challenge for enterprise intelligent marketing. This case study aims to guide students to think about how enterprises in the metaverse era can reasonably layout virtual digital spokespersons and effectively manage their relationship with real celebrity spokespersons and virtual anchors.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人工智能营销》、《网络营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化身营销理论；恐怖谷理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
